Robo Tab is a simple but effective new tab extension for your Chrome browser, which also provides quick links to popular social media websites. Once you install this extension your browser new tab will feature a search box with search results by Microsoft Bing.

By Clicking ‘Add to Chrome’, you are accepting and agreeing to install the Robo Tab extension, and understand that your browsers new tab will be changed to that provided by the service with search results by Microsoft Bing. Your usage of this extension will be governed by the Privacy Policy and Terms & Conditions links below. 

Intelligent, powerful and independent…what else do you need from a new tab?
